## func Compare

```go
func Compare[T any](a, b T, less LessFn[T]) int
```

Compare uses a less function to determine the ordering of 'a' and 'b'\. It returns:

\* \-1 if a \< b

\* 1 if a \> b

\* 0 if a == b
